quran[60]{c,v,t}:
  51,1,“. Ndikulumbilira mphepo imene ikubalalitsa mitambo ya mvula
  51,2,“Ndi imene imasenza mitolo yolemera (ya madzi)
  51,3,“Ndi kuyenda (nawo madziwo) mwaubwino
  51,4,“Ndi awo amene amagawa rizq (limene Allah amalipereka kwa amene wamfuna)
  51,5,"“Ndithu zimene mukulonjezedwa nzoonadi, (zidzachitika)"
  51,6,"“Ndipo, ndithu malipiro (pa zochita zanu) adzapezekadi"
  51,7,“Ndikulumbilira thambo lomwe njira zake zambiri nzoikidwa mwaluso
  51,8,"“Ndithu inu muli m’mau otsutsana, (pa zimene mukunena)"
  51,9,“(Kupyolera m’mawu amenewa) akuchotsedwa ku icho (chikhulupiliro chalonjezo loona) amene adachotsedwa (ku chikhulupilirocho)
  51,10,“Aonongeka abodza (amene akunena za tsiku lachiweruziro mongoganizira)
  51,11,"“Iwo amene akubira mu umbuli, osalabadira (za tsiku lachimaliziro)"
  51,12,“Akufunsa (mwachipongwe ponena kuti) “Lidzakhala liti tsiku lamalipiro?”
  51,13,“(Limenelo ndi) tsiku lomwe iwo adzalangidwa ku Moto
  51,14,"“(Adzawauza kuti): “Lawani chilango chanu ichi chimene munkachifulumizitsa (kuti chikufikeni).”"
  51,15,“Ndithu oopa (Allah) adzakhala (akusangalala) m’minda ndi mu akasupe okongola
  51,16,“Uku akulandira zimene wawapatsa Mbuye wawo (malipiro aulemu); ndithu iwo ankachita zabwino asanapeze izi
  51,17,“Nthawi yausiku amagona pang’ono. (Amadzuka nachita mapemphero mochulukitsa)
  51,18,"“Ndipo kum’bandakucha, iwo amapempha chikhululuko"
  51,19,“Ndipo m’chuma chawo mudali gawo (lodziwika) la opempha ndi osapempha (mwa osauka)
  51,20,"“M’nthaka muli zizindikiro kwa otsimikiza, (zosonyeza kuti Allah alipo)"
  51,21,“Ndi mwa inu nomwe; kodi simuona
  51,22,"“Ndipo kumwamba kuli zokuthandizani (pa moyo wanu), ndi zimene mukulonjezedwa"
  51,23,"“Ndikulumbilira Mbuye wa kumwamba ndi pansi, ndithu zimenezo ndi zoona monga kulili kuyankhula kwanu"
  51,24,“Kodi yakufika nkhani ya alendo a Ibrahim; (angelo) olemekezeka
  51,25,"“Pamene adalowa kwa iye ndi kunena kuti: “Salaam,” (“Mtendere”)! Iye adayankha: “Salaam,” (“Mtendere) inu ndinu anthu osadziwika (achilendo).”"
  51,26,"“Adatembenukira kwa akunyumba ake (mwakachetechete), ndipo adadza ndi nyama ya mwana wa ng’ombe yonona (yowotcha)"
  51,27,"“Naipereka kwa iwo (koma sadadye); iye adanena (modabwa): “Kodi bwanji simukudya?”"
  51,28,"“Mumtima mwake adadzazidwa mantha ndi iwo. Iwo adati: “Usaope,” ndipo adamuuza nkhani yabwino ya kubala mwana wodziwa"
  51,29,"“Adadza mkazi wake ndi mkuwe (pamene adamva nkhani yabwino ija). Adadzimenya kunkhope (ndi dzanja lake kusonyeza kudabwa ndi kusatheka). Ndipo adati: (“Ine ndine) nkhalamba (ndiponso) chumba; (ndingabereke bwanji)?”"
  51,30,"“Iwo adati: “Momwemo, Mbuye wako wanena. Iye Ngwanzeru zakuya (pa chilichonse chimene akulamula); Ngodziwa; (palibe chimene chingabisike kwa Iye)"
  51,31,"“۞ (Ibrahim) adati: “Kodi nkhani yanu ndiyotani E inu otumidwa?”"
  51,32,"“Iwo adati: “Tatumizidwa kwa anthu oipa.”"
  51,33,““Kuti tiwagende ndi miyala yotenthedwa kuchokera kudongo.”
  51,34,““Yoikidwa chizindikiro cha aliyense wochimwa kuchokera kwa Mbuye wako.”
  51,35,“Tidawatulutsa okhulupirira omwe adali m’mudzimo
  51,36,“Sitidapeze mmenemo (okhulupirira ambiri) kupatula mnyumba imodzi ya Asilamu
  51,37,“Ndipo tidasiya pamenepo chizindikiro (chosonyeza kuonongeka kwa eni mudziwo kuti chikhale lingaliro) kwa amene akuopa chilango chopweteka
  51,38,“M’nkhani ya Mûsa (muli phunziro) pamene tidamtuma kwa Farawo uku atalimbikitsidwa ndi chisonyezo choonekera
  51,39,"“Koma Farawo adanyoza (kukhulupirira Mûsa) chifukwa chotama nyonga zake, ndipo adati: “Uyu ndi wamatsenga kapena wamisala.”"
  51,40,“Tidamlanga pamodzi ndi khamu lake la nkhondo ndi kuwaponya mnyanja; iye ali wodzudzulidwa
  51,41,“Ndipo m’nkhani ya Âdi (muli phunziro) pamene tidawatumizira chimphepo (chamkuntho) chopanda chabwino mkati mwake
  51,42,“Chomwe sichisiya chinthu chimene chachidutsa koma kuchichita monga chofumbwa
  51,43,"“Ndipo m’nkhani ya Samudu (muli chisonyezo) pamene kudanenedwa kwa iwo kuti: “Sangalalani (mnyumba zanu) mpaka nthawi yaikika.”"
  51,44,“Koma adadzikweza (ponyozera) lamulo la Mbuye wawo. Choncho chiphokoso chidawaononga uku akupenya
  51,45,“Sadathe kuimilira ndi (kuthawa) ndiponso sadali wodzipulumutsa
  51,46,“Naonso anthu a Nuh (tidawaononga) kale chifukwa iwo adali anthu otuluka mchilamulo (cha Allah)
  51,47,“Thambo tidalimanga mwamphamvu (ndi luntha); ndipo tingathe kuchita zochuluka (kuposa zimenezi)
  51,48,“Ndipo nthaka tidaiyala; taonani kukonza bwino Ife amene tidakonza nthaka
  51,49,“Ndipo m’chinthu chilichonse talenga ziwiriziwiri kuti inu mulingalire (ndi kukhulupirira mphamvu Zathu)
  51,50,“Thawirani kwa Allah. Ine ndine mchenjezi woonekera kwa inu wochokera kwa Iye
  51,51,“Ndipo musadzipangire mulungu wina wompembedza ndi kumuphatikiza ndi Allah. Ndithu ine ndine mchenjezi woonekera poyera kwa inu wochokera kwa Iye
  51,52,"“Momwemo (ndimo idalili mibadwo yakale pamodzi ndi aneneri awo); palibe Mthenga amene adawadzera anthu akale, anthu akowa kulibe, popanda kumnena kuti: “Ndiwamatsenga kapena wamisala.”"
  51,53,"“Kodi adalangizana za mawuwa pakati pawo? Iyayi, koma iwo ndianthu opyola malire"
  51,54,"“Choncho apatukire iwo (amakani), iwe suli wodzudzulidwa (pakuleka kwawo kuyankha kuitana)"
  51,55,“Kumbutsa. Ndithu kukumbutsa kumawathandiza okhulupirira
  51,56,“Sindidalenge ziwanda (majini) ndi anthu koma kuti azindipembedza
  51,57,“Sindifuna kwa iwo chithandizo ndiponso sindifuna kuti azindidyetsa
  51,58,"“Ndithu Allah ndi Amene amapereka rizq; Iye ndi Mwini mphamvu zoposa; Wolimba, (salaphera kanthu)"
  51,59,“Ndithu amene adzichitira okha chinyengo (pokana ndi kutsutsa) ali nalo gawo la chilango monga gawo la anzawo (a mibadwo yakale); choncho asandifulumizitse (kutsitsa chilango nthawi yake isanafike)
  51,60,“Kuonongeka kuli pa amene atsutsa za tsiku lawo limene alonjezedwa